pageProduct.name: Wagner Lecithin 1200 100 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

This formula;
Helps to maintain cellular structures
Helps to break down the fats in the body
Supports a healthy liver

Features
Lecithin is a complex mixture of phospholipids.
It plays a role in the maintenance of cell membrane integrity, which is vital to all basic biological processes.
Lecithin also assists in the breakdown and distribution of fats in the digestive system, and it supports your liver health.
This formulation is in an easy to swallow soft gel capsule.

Ingredients

Each capsule provides
Lecithin  1.2g
